      "content": "i dont even know why im talking to u. i was looking at my studio today and it just felt like... a graveyard. i cant paint anymore. every time i pick up a brush it feels like i'm trying to paint with nothing. there's just nothing inside of me. like the person who used to live here is gone and there's just this empty shell left. it's actually kind of terrifying how quiet it is in my head.",
